<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jul/27/">&#x27a0;</a> July 27, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="google_code_pro" >

        
        <a name="002760"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://code.google.com/hosting/">Google Code - Project Hosting</a></h4>

        

        <p>Google offer free Subversion hosting and bug tracking for open-source projects.  Missing in comparison to Sourceforge:  Web Hosting, Downloads, SVN web-browsing and adverts galore.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
