<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jul/11/">&#x27a0;</a> July 11, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="roundcube_webma" >

        
        <a name="002683"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.roundcube.net/">RoundCube Webmail Project</a></h4>

        

        <p>Attractive, and fairly lightweight, self-hostable webmail client.  Works with any IMAP server.</p>

